<div class="pdbpage"><div class="contentWrapper"><div class="pdbTopBlock"><img src="http://www.ozy.com/pictures/120xany/5/3/1/5531_Inside-Camp-David_1_1.jpg" class="author" data-image-tablet="248xany" data-image-desktop="312xany" alt="Camp David" /><header><h1>The Presidential Daily Brief</h1><p class="byline"><span class="date">October 06, 2013</span></p><p>Camp David Edition</p></header><!--
